  "description": {
   "en": "Get ready for hot tea and hotter action in this tale of opposites attracting on the tatami mats. Poor Tokumaru Madoka is just a regular energetic guy that can't seem to go even five minutes without breaking something. One day, his hapless sister has had enough, and she forces him to join their high school's Tea Ceremony Club, hoping to instill a little discipline in her hopeless klutz of a brother.  \n  \nTea Ceremony Club president Hasune Kazuma is Tokumaru's complete opposite. The tall, dark president is the pinnacle of restraint, having been taught from a young age how to uphold his family's traditions. The sophisticated president and his awkward pupil conceal a brewing attraction, but they can't avoid steaming each other up. Even full to the brim with passion, will the two of them be able to bridge their differences and get along with each other?",
   "pl": "Można stwierdzić, że Tokumaru ma dwie lewe ręce. Jest niezwykle niezdarny. Do tego stopnia, że kiedy niszczy należącą do młodszej siostry ramkę ze zdjęciem jej ukochanego, ta wpada w szał i stwierdza: nauczę cię spokoju i wdzięku, nawet gdyby miało cię to zabić - po czym wysyła go do klubu herbacianego. W klubie tym rządy sprawuje Hasune i za swój osobisty cel ustanawia sobie wyprowadzenie Tokumaru na ludzi. Dla tego z kolei oznacza to początek kłopotów i drogi przez męki. Ale może znajomość z Hasune nie okaże się tak straszna, jak na początku sądził?"
  },
